text: Brigitte Kiesler (15 August 1924 - 10 May 2013) was a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2013 deaths Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ludwigslust
